      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "One major argument is the potential for loss of human control as AI systems become more autonomous and powerful. Unaligned superintelligence could pursue goals detrimental to human well-being, leading to unintended catastrophic outcomes. Furthermore, the risk includes the possibility of misuse, where advanced AI could be weaponized or used for large-scale societal manipulation. Therefore, proactive regulation is argued to ensure AI development remains safely aligned with human values and limits potential existential threats.",
